pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">While</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> constitutional review </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">could exist and function without a</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> Bill of Rights</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">, it</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> would be severely curtailed</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">. </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">Traditionally, </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">co</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">nstitutional review</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">ensures</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> the protection of</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">fundamental rights and freedoms. Indeed, w</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">ithout</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> a</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> Bill of R</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">ights</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">, the courts </span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt">would only be able to ensure</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> compliance with the</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> procedural requirements of the</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> legislative procedures or</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> the</span><span style="font-family:'Minion Pro'; font-size:12pt"> </span><span style="f